name: testBranchSourcesOptionsList
description: All options are displayed from 'Add source'

testStage.description: All options are displayed from 'Add source'

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Configure' button on side menu
Click on the 'Configure' Button on the Base Job Page
Click on the 'Add Source' button from the Configuration page
Get an options list from the 'Add Source' drop down menu
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
